<simpara>Read <link xl:href="https://daggerok.github.io/kafka-examples">project reference documentation</link></simpara>
<simpara><emphasis>getting kafka up and running</emphasis></simpara>
<formalpara>
<title>requires sdkman</title>
<para>
<screen>curl -s 'https://get.sdkman.io' | zsh
source ${HOME}/.sdkman/bin/sdkman-init.sh
sdk install springboot 2.0.4.RELEASE
spring install org.springframework.cloud:spring-cloud-cli:2.0.0.RELEASE
spring cloud kafka</screen>
</para>
</formalpara>
<formalpara>
<title>requires docker</title>
<para>
<screen>./mvnw -Pdocker docker-compose:up
# play!
./mvnw -Pdocker docker-compose:down</screen>
</para>
</formalpara>
